{"comments":"Element Context — What atoms apply to what elements.\n\n## Architecture\n\nAt 10,000 tokens/second, an agent configuring UI needs:\n1. Immediate comprehension — What can I modify here?\n2. Bounded choices — The RIGHT atoms for this element type\n3. Composable layers — Surface → Material → Motion → Haptics\n4. Zero ambiguity — Same config = same output\n\nElementContext defines the **property signature** of any element:\nwhat property groups apply, how they're organized, and their bounds.\n\n## Property Groups\n\nProperties are organized into logical groups for human and agent UX:\n\n- **Appearance**: Color, Shape, Typography\n- **Surface**: Material, Texture, Roughness, Metalness\n- **Effects**: Glow, Shadow, Elevation, Blur\n- **Motion**: Paths, Keyframes (always bounded start/end)\n- **Interaction**: Haptics, Gestures, Cursor\n- **Diffusion**: Noise conditioning for texture synthesis\n\n## NO INFINITE LOOPS\n\nMotion paths ALWAYS have:\n- Start keyframe (required)\n- End keyframe (required)\n- Iteration count (bounded Int, never infinite)\n\nThis is enforced at the type level.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"GroupAppearance"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"GroupSurface"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[137,3]},"title":"GroupEffects"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[138,3]},"title":"GroupMotion"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[139,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[139,3]},"title":"GroupInteraction"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[140,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[140,3]},"title":"GroupDiffusion"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Context"],"PropertyGroup"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[142,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[142,1]},"title":"eqPropertyGroup"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Context"],"PropertyGroup"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[143,1]},"title":"ordPropertyGroup"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Context"],"PropertyGroup"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Context.purs","start":[145,1]},"title":"showPropertyGroup"}],"comments":"Logical groupings of properties for UI organization.\n\nProperties are grouped by domain, not by Schema pillar. This optimizes\nfor human comprehension: \"I want to change how this looks\" → Appearance,\n\"I want to animate it\" → Motion.\n","info":{"dataDeclType"